      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the difference between ISO week numbers and US week numbers?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "ISO 8601 weeks start on Monday and week 1 is the week containing the first Thursday. US weeks traditionally start on Sunday and week 1 is simply the week containing January 1. The two systems can differ by 1 week, especially in early January and late December." } },
